---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Admissions" lang="fr" description="Postulez a Forest International School Paris - Processus d'admission et exigences">
  <!-- Hero Section with Image -->
  <section class="relative py-20 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/images/children-diversity.jpg" alt="Enfants a Forest International School" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1e3d29]/95 via-[#2d5a3d]/80 to-[#2d5a3d]/60"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm mb-6 border border-[#c9a962]/30">Rejoignez-nous</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Admissions</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
          Nous accueillons des familles du monde entier. Decouvrez notre processus d'admission et comment postuler.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Admissions Process -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[#faf8f5]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] font-semibold text-sm mb-4">Comment Postuler</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Processus d'Admission</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">
          Notre processus d'admission est concu pour assurer une bonne adequation entre l'ecole et l'eleve.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#4a7c5c] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              1
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29] mb-2">Inscrivez-vous a une Journee Portes Ouvertes</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Inscrivez-vous a l'une de nos prochaines Journees Portes Ouvertes pour visiter l'ecole et rencontrer notre equipe.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#4a7c5c] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              2
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29] mb-2">Soumettez Votre Candidature</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Soumettez une candidature avec les documents requis pour l'inscription.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#4a7c5c] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              3
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29] mb-2">Contact de l'Equipe d'Admission</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Un membre de l'equipe d'admission vous contactera pour definir les prochaines etapes du processus.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#4a7c5c] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              4
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29] mb-2">Visite de l'Ecole</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Rejoignez-nous pour une visite en personne ou une reunion virtuelle pour en savoir plus sur nos programmes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 5 -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#c9a962] to-[#d4b872] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              5
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow flex-grow border-2 border-[#c9a962]">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29] mb-2">Acceptation & Inscription</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Apres acceptation, nous confirmerons la place de votre enfant a FISP et vous guiderons dans l'inscription.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Information -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 rounded-full text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm mb-4">Bon a Savoir</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Informations Cles</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-3xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#4a7c5c] rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-lg mb-3">Candidatures Toute l'Annee</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Les candidatures peuvent etre soumises tout au long de l'annee scolaire.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-3xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4a7c5c] to-[#2d5a3d] rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-lg mb-3">Pas de Liste d'Attente</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Nous preferons ne pas avoir de listes d'attente. Contactez-nous pour verifier la disponibilite.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-3xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#c9a962] to-[#d4b872] rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-lg mb-3">Tranche d'Age</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Maternelle (2 ans) au College (jusqu'a 15 ans). Pas de date limite d'anniversaire.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#1e3d29]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 rounded-full text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm mb-6 border border-[#c9a962]/30">Commencez</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Pret a Postuler?</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Contactez notre equipe d'admission pour commencer le processus de candidature ou planifier une visite.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/fr/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-[#2d5a3d] font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors shadow-lg">
          Contacter les Admissions
        </a>
        <a href="/fr/tuition" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-transparent text-white font-bold rounded-full border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-[#2d5a3d] transition-colors">
          Voir les Frais
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
